      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example is mechanically robust, with the Double VANOS system serviced and the rear subframe proactively reinforced to ensure structural integrity under high torque loads. The drivetrain remains tight, benefiting from a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential that provides exceptional traction. The suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein dampers and poly-bushing kits, maintaining the precise turn-in and communicative chassis feedback characteristic of the E46 platform. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals are optimized for performance, with consistent compression and a clean oil analysis history.",
